{"tid":2186964,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【18年已知情夫細So存在】Macy感激老公忍受「共妻」生活: 佢一直等待，等我認清一切","createTime":"2020-09-03T10:27:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T02:30:49.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"0b5aa3fbe3a3e2b79019c58cf78321e9282a4d42","tid":2186964,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:27:58.000Z","msg":"節錄:<br />\n18年阿Wing發現姦情<br />\nMacy的剖白中，除了她老公，原來細So的老婆阿Wing，也是18年已發現枕邊人不忠，且早已鎖定第三者是Macy。坦白的Macy說:「18年10月左右，佢太太發現，佢都只係叫我block咗佢太太ig。」<br />\n阿Wing有否主動找她攤牌，Macy:「無，發現當日佢(細So)解決咗佢嗰邊之後，都有立即打畀我，同我講話只係畀我安心，就算太太知道咗，佢都用咗好多大話呃咗佢，佢唔會離開我。我知道當時So係話同我從來無見過面，同埋其他方法同佢講，但佢點交代我就唔清楚。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_757681_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_757681_0&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hTvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=9cd83e2b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_757681_0&h=8a8e5418\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_757681_0</a>"},{"pid":"34c5212255e30a24f7ade4ce1dd90a8605555a2d","tid":2186964,"uid":127929,"like":22,"dislike":4,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FCWv9kf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFCWv9kf.png&h=933fc960&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3288f8dfd345a129526ee6093736f3b9f6e35f3e","tid":2186964,"uid":28068,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:37:45.000Z","msg":"阿b個老公同細so老婆<br />\n呢d人應該係值得讚定係on9?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad584eb32317a1ff7b715d7fc9fb5ab59f5fa4cc","tid":2186964,"uid":85586,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:38:38.000Z","msg":"不如佢哋交換結婚算啦反正大家都有共同癖好<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a3cea27933fa9d2f8bb2373f3f97e151b234a3","tid":2186964,"uid":55519,"like":